{"tid":2157122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞打破咗74年唻嘅記錄！","createTime":"2020-08-14T21:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T22:06:21.000Z","uid":201949,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e08605f8ab8e0f543661e3d403ee49fdfd0b64","tid":2157122,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:55:24.000Z","msg":"對上一次巴塞俾人單場入8球已經係1946年嘅事！<br />\n而嗰陣時嘅正值佛朗哥嘅統治時代，加泰隆尼亞不斷受打壓。而喺好出名嘅嘅11:3嗰場El Clasico （派國家的保安官員訪問巴塞，然後威迫利誘。在生命受到威脅之下，巴塞球員就範，在次回合，皇馬以11:1大勝巴塞），只不過係早三年嘅時。當時嘅巴塞唔單只球員受威脅，連轉會市場都受壓，買賣球員都受影響，成隊波陷入低迷。<br />\n<br />\n而今時今日嘅巴塞，有錢、有美斯、球員冇被迫害，到底都點撚樣踢先可以踢到咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同一隊球，可以喺太平盛世嘅年代踢到同被迫害時代一樣，執柒咗佢嘅屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3a57722f953b57dab5ebb3fde5d66b636ba156","tid":2157122,"uid":219128,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uutr4fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUutr4fd.png&h=b792f335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69325c76433740202eec1f5e858385037f9dbde4","tid":2157122,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:57:04.000Z","msg":"烏迪迪中左肺炎唔計啦"},{"pid":"02427cc051ab0c021e07bd64187066722d282511","tid":2157122,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:58:44.000Z","msg":"見好多巴迷都死攬美斯，我並唔同意<br />\n隊長都啞火，其他點睇你頭？美斯係就係仲有貨交，仲心態上真係差啲。<br />\n美斯我仲好愛你咖，但你自己都可唔可以爭氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbe41a6ed02d660a06356a6954f0e01206e34ee","tid":2157122,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69325c76433740202eec1f5e858385037f9dbde4","tid":2157122,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:57:04.000Z","msg":"烏迪迪中左肺炎唔計啦